subtests.name: Importing a same-origin script with the default WorkletOptions should omit the credentials
Importing a remote-origin script with the default WorkletOptions should not include the credentials
Importing a same-origin script with credentials=omit should omit the credentials
Importing a remote-origin script with credentials=omit should omit the credentials
Importing a same-origin script with credentials=same-origin should include the credentials
Importing a remote-origin script with credentials=same-origin should not include the credentials
Importing a same-origin script with credentials=include should include the credentials
Importing a remote-origin script with credentials=include should include the credentials
